                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8511" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1314</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2077 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">涟漪纷纷，波澜不止——*ST新亿的陨落</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Ripples Abound, Waves Ceaseless——the Fall of *ST Xinyi</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张倩，吉祎宁，林姣姣，董晓晗</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黑龙江科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新疆亿路万源实业控股股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">*ST；退市新规；强制退市；财务造假</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">*ST; New delisting regulations; Mandatory delisting; Financial fraud</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着我国资本市场基础制度体系的不断完善，市场资源配置得到优化，资本市场秩序趋于健康发展，但我国资本市场的改革仍然面临着公司上市难、退市难的主要问题。退市制度先后进行了四次改革，从初始建立期发展到现在的成熟期，在诸多法律标准的铺垫以及相关部门的努力下，我国于2021年正式推出了新的退市制度。沪深交易所实行了强制退市的多元化指标体系，简化了退市流程，将退市监管进一步严格化。本案例描述了新疆亿路万源实业控股股份有限公司（以下简称*ST新亿）的发展始末，通过梳理*ST新亿自身的发展历程以及新规出台后*ST新亿被上交所强制退市的故事，引导学员理解*ST新亿进行财务舞弊的方式以及多次财务造假的动机。案例旨在帮助学生了解我国退市制度的发展历程，引领学生思考*ST新亿的退市缘由和公司退市对市场和相关企业产生的影响，借此提高学员识别与防范财务舞弊的能力，为其他上市公司防范退市风险提供借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With continuous improvement of basic system of China&#39;s capital market, allocation of market resources has been optimized, and order of capital market has tended to develop healthily, but main reform direction of capital market is still to solve difficulty of listing and delisting of companies. The delisting system has been reformed four times, from initial establishment period to current maturity period, and new delisting system has been implemented since 2021. Shanghai and Shenzhen Exchanges optimized the diversified index system for forced delisting, simplified the delisting process, and further tightened delisting supervision. This case describes whole process of development of Xinjiang Yilu Wangyuan Idustrial Investment Holding Co., Ltd (hereinafter referred to as *ST XinYi ) , sorts out the forced delisting history of *ST XinYi by Shanghai Stock Exchange after introduction of new regulations, and guides students to understand motivation and behavior of financial fraud many times. The case aims to help students understand the development process of delisting system, lead students to think about reasons for delisting of *ST XinYi and impact of new delisting regulations on the company, and provide reference for other listed companies to prevent delisting risks.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理理论与实务》、《财务会计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">退市新规；舞弊风险因子理论；财务造假的基本手段；内部人控制理论；财务造假的识别与防范</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
